<tr id="L313"><td><a href="#L313">313</a></td><td>WINN [on monitor]:  Oh, but I do. Bareil just made a surprise announcement to the Vedek Assembly. He's withdrawn himself from the Choosing. He no longer wishes to be the next Kai. I know this is painful for you, child, but you've done a great service for all of Bajor. Whoever is chosen tomorrow as the new Kai will owe you a debt of gratitude. May the Prophets guide you.</td></tr>

<tr id="L314"><td><a href="#L314">314</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: end transmission.</td></tr>

